This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the generation of facial composites. It also involves the use of generative and evolutionary computation, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the interactive nature of the system, which could fall under the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves the creation of high-resolution images, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
